{
  "chapter": 39,
  "chapter_summary": "快活王率众围困沈浪、熊猫儿、朱七七、王怜花与独孤伤于洞窟之中。快活王以金蚕毒蜂相威胁，提出以独孤伤人头换取其余人活命的条件。沈浪与熊猫儿断然拒绝，宁死不弃友。独孤伤深受感动，为不连累众人，毅然撞壁自尽，临终感言\"得一知己，死而无憾\"。快活王兑现诺言放众人出洞，但洞窟如迷宫，众人饥渴交加，数次迷路。沈浪凭智慧最终找到出路。出洞后快活王在洞口设酒相候，与沈浪英雄对饮，惺惺相惜。快活王暗中派三十名骑士跟踪，又在溪水中放入牲畜污染水源。王怜花为求生竟饮污水，众人继续沿溪逃亡。快活王对沈浪赞叹不已，感慨\"既生本王，为何又生沈浪\"。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只因无论火烧水淹都太平凡，太普通了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "平凡？普通？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但愿她不会。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她要咱们死，却又要咱们死得口服心服。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你倒很了解她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事至如今我已不能不了解她。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她真的这么了不起？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她的确是个不平凡的女子，这点谁也不能否认。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜她不在这里，否则她听见你的话，一定会很高兴，是么，是么……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快了！真的快了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_shang",
      "speaker_name": "独孤伤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁……来的是谁？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "猜不出的……你们永远猜不出的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也猜不出。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_shang",
      "speaker_name": "独孤伤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快……快……活王！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很好，你居然还记得本王。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到吧，本王竟在这里寻着你们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你怎……怎会知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这只因他还是人，还有人性，而你，你……你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "岂敢岂敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多谢夸奖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜你做出的却都是傻事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实，我本也不太愿意和你作对的，只要你放了我，我……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你现在才说这话，已太迟了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些天来，你瘦了，瘦了许多。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这话是什么意思？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我这话是什么意思，你本该清楚得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可贺可喜？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位永远不会知道各位若是死了，本王有多么伤心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你在放屁么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为何还不下手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_shang",
      "speaker_name": "独孤伤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你究竟想怎样？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位真的想听么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你当真杀了我，你一定会后悔的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本王从不后悔。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的？真的不后悔……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，你不妨试试，你只管杀吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪，你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我放心得很，我知道你暂时还不想杀我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你们其实还有两条路走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两条路？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那第二条路呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个时辰？真的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还是你知道本王的心意。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么条件？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只要一个人的人头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你要杀的是独孤伤……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你为何定要逼我们做这种绝情绝义的事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪也和他一样，不能让你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要问的只是沈浪的意见，不是你的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王怜花，我希望你知道一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我在听着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你该知道我并不像你这样怕死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪毕竟是沈浪，我熊猫儿总算没有看错。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗡嗡",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好，金蚕毒蜂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哧！哧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个'弹指神通'。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你如今才知道厉害么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不行，无论如何，我也不能容人伤他。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪你难道真的也和他一样呆？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有时我比熊猫儿还呆。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也情愿陪独孤伤一起死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但那是另外一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_shang",
      "speaker_name": "独孤伤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你这呆子，你何必！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_shang",
      "speaker_name": "独孤伤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们既能做呆子，我为何不能……但你们却莫要忘记，我是为你们而死的，你们就得为我活下去，好好活下去……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本王绝世之才，纵然我是一个人独来独去，天下之人又有谁能奈何得了本王，何况……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦！他是谁？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出来呀，本王又未阻拦你等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你想……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王，快活王……慢走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "糟糕，咱们上了他的当了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "的确糟透。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是活活饿死在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有了主意？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拿灯过来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要能找出这三条路哪一条是活路就好了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "油尽灯枯了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你难道也无法可想？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们是老鼠么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然不是。你有法子了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，还不快走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不要王怜花跟在我后面，我不要拉他的手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然是我断后。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但猫儿你可得小心了，有这样的人走在你后面，你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这种事可不能以常理衡度，你还是要小心些好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 546
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人……唉，女人的心……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "女人的心怎样？总比你好得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫忘了，若不是我，你和沈浪……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我希望你知道，做一个好人，总比做坏人快乐得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的没有走错？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他决不会错的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别人对沈浪可没有你对沈浪这么强的信心。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你不信任，他为何不自己走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来时有人引路，自然走得快些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是呀，难道这点你都想不到么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪错了么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……他不会……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "错了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家的性命俱在此，兄台可不能将之视如儿戏。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对了，我早就说过，你可以自己走呀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，不如由王兄你来领路如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你累了吧，歇歇好么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不累，不累，真的不累，快走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好孩子，你真乖。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要听你这一句话，就算累死也没什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但却没有人向我说这样的话，我累死岂非冤枉。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你为何不在这里歇下？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此时此刻，又有什么法子好想。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天知道这其中有什么差错。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 648,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，迟早总会走出去的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "完了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "究竟是什么？为何完了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是我方才抛在地上的铜灯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道……难道咱们又走回方才的地方了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，看来这已是咱们的葬身之处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说完了？咱们有救了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 672,
      "line_end": 672
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有……有救？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要再回到这里，咱们就有救了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你说的什么话，我不懂。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "方才咱们路并没有走错，只是方向错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是什么话，我更不懂了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，真的有救了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你现在才知道沈浪不错么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们总算逃出来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 708
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们还没有逃出去，这不过刚刚是开始。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 710,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚开始？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 712
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下怎能令阁下失望。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上还有人走不出的路么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 744
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你再不走，就……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 792,
      "line_end": 792
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个时辰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 800
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个时辰，决不会少，也决不会多，滚吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 802,
      "line_end": 802
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在别人身上受了气，何苦拿我来出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 804
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能和你在一起的，自然都不会是普通人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你放心，必定快得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 818,
      "line_end": 818
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许，我生下来便是为了要和你作对的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 832,
      "line_end": 832
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王爷，我……我说错了什么？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 860,
      "line_end": 860
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你我能饮此一杯，已非易事……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 878,
      "line_end": 878
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此……请！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 884,
      "line_end": 884
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 886,
      "line_end": 886
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既生本王，为何又生沈浪？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 904,
      "line_end": 904
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咄，去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 906,
      "line_end": 906
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "绝世的英雄？他也能算英雄？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 918,
      "line_end": 918
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "英雄，英雄……有时我真不懂，'英雄'这两字，究竟有没有定义，如果有，谁又能为我解释……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 924,
      "line_end": 924
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有人能为你解释的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 926,
      "line_end": 926
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我渴死了，沈浪，求求你，找点水给我喝好么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 932,
      "line_end": 932
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还是沈浪好，他总算喝了杯酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 934,
      "line_end": 934
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你嫉妒？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 936,
      "line_end": 936
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "猫嘴里终究还是吐不出象牙来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 950,
      "line_end": 950
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位还能开得出玩笑，佩服佩服。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 952,
      "line_end": 952
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道什么，现在才是最需要开玩笑的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 954,
      "line_end": 954
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "话虽不错，但你我已只有一个时辰。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 964,
      "line_end": 964
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要好生利用，一个时辰也不算短。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 966,
      "line_end": 966
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，现在……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 968,
      "line_end": 968
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 982,
      "line_end": 982
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "属下和二十九个弟兄，都已遵照王爷的吩咐，寻好藏身之处，有的伏在草丛中，有的爬到树梢头，有的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 984,
      "line_end": 984
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些本王难道不知道，废话少说。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 986,
      "line_end": 986
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈浪这小子简直不是个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 992,
      "line_end": 992
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那熊猫儿如何？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 994,
      "line_end": 994
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们难道没有惊慌奔跑？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1002,
      "line_end": 1002
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们慢慢走的，像是一点也不着急。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1004,
      "line_end": 1004
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王叹道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1012,
      "line_end": 1012
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有沈浪这样的对手，当真可怕得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1018,
      "line_end": 1018
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你莫忘了他的对手是谁！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1020,
      "line_end": 1020
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此刻他们往哪里去了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1026,
      "line_end": 1026
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来仿佛是走向溪水。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1028,
      "line_end": 1028
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到了到了，幸好这里还有条小溪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1036,
      "line_end": 1036
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1046,
      "line_end": 1046
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他会不会在水中下毒？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1052,
      "line_end": 1052
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这点你们可放心，活水之中，根本无法下毒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1054,
      "line_end": 1054
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有关下毒的事，王怜花自然比谁都清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1056,
      "line_end": 1056
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这一次，但愿你的直觉不灵才好。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1064,
      "line_end": 1064
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_nv",
      "speaker_name": "牧女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快活王，计谋高，小沈浪，上当了，眼看水，喝不了，急得猫儿直跳脚，气得沈浪满地跑……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1082,
      "line_end": 1082
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说的不错吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1084,
      "line_end": 1084
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恶贼，畜生！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1086,
      "line_end": 1086
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么缺德的主意，也亏他想得出。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1088,
      "line_end": 1088
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你敢喝这种水，这水里有尿你知不知道？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1092,
      "line_end": 1092
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……但你……你竟真的……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1098,
      "line_end": 1098
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_lang",
      "speaker_name": "沈浪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此刻我虽还不致如此，但你们……你们……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1110,
      "line_end": 1110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_qi_qi",
      "speaker_name": "朱七七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我宁可死也不喝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1112,
      "line_end": 1112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_mao_er",
      "speaker_name": "熊猫儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也没有这本事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1114,
      "line_end": 1114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lian_hua",
      "speaker_name": "王怜花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫要忘记，时候已不多了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1118,
      "line_end": 1118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "启禀王爷，他们已到了溪水旁了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1122,
      "line_end": 1122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可笑那脸色发白的小子，居然连尿都喝，而且……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1136,
      "line_end": 1136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王怜花喝了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1138,
      "line_end": 1138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他……他喝了不少。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1140,
      "line_end": 1140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但这小子连尿都喝，有什么出息？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1146,
      "line_end": 1146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此番他们又是如何走法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1164,
      "line_end": 1164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们沿着溪水，还是缓缓的在走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1166,
      "line_end": 1166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kuai_huo_wang",
      "speaker_name": "快活王",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们竟还不躲藏？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 39,
      "line_start": 1168,
      "line_end": 1168
    }
  ],
